// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2021-0896 — Mass File Rename (spook)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 23799662-4f66-56c3-bd42-0a99c756bf0e

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
